snippet.title: Best VGM 2348 - Resident Evil 4 - Regenerator
snippet.description:
See also;
Best VGM 826 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NVRgpAmkmPg

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

GameCube / PS2 / PC / Wii / Etc.
Resident Evil 4 (2005)
Regenerator
Misao Senbongi & Shusaku Uchiyama
